Hi Guys, I see the blog listing have this IF condition. Just wondering if module.display_for_each_list_item is a reserved variable?

See the sample below

```{% if module.display_for_each_list_item.index("description") &gt;= 0 %}
  {% set show_description = true %}
{% endif %}```
```{% if module.display_for_each_list_item.index("button") &gt;= 0 %}
  {% set show_button = false %}
{% endif %}```
